Show HN: Hot Reload for Unity – Edit any C# code, get immediate updates in game
text:
Hey HN!

We're a game studio working with the Unity engine, and have spent many hours frustrated, waiting for code changes to compile. It was taking us 1-2 minutes for the every single change. So we developed a solution! We created a tool that lets us iterate changes in less than 1 second, without waiting for Unity to compile or reload the game.

We've been using this tool in our studio for a few years now and it's been a game changer for us; saving massive amounts of frustration, and also helping us hit deadlines. We recently decided to make it public and share it with the wider community, while also helping us fund our future projects.

It's free for Unity Personal users, and Unity Plus/Pro/Enterprise users can get a 30-day free trial followed by free 2 hours a day of usage until purchase (after which case it’s unlimited usage, no restrictions).

We hope this tool can help other developers too! Let us know what you think!

Viral Instagram Scam, account Hacked – Any Recourse?
text:
Well folks, it finally happened: I fell for one of those “Hey buddy I got a new album, click this link” scams.

The person quickly sent up an Authenticator 2FA. Beyond the shock/embarrassment of being fooled, and 19 stages of denial (“I’m a DEV! How dare they?!”), what I find absolutely bizarre is: The video verification doesn’t recognize me, no other recovery method seems to exist. Are there truly no options with Instagram to get the account back although my phone/email?
